.006 both intake and exaust. Used to be .004 intake, .006 exaust but the
general consensus is that .006 works just fine.

	Can someone tell me what the valve gap should be on a 1600dp
engine?  I want to run down and get a feeler gauge I have seemed to have
lost mine.





